+#!/usr/bin/env python2.6
+## begin license ##
+# 
+# "Solr Run" starts Solr with correct parameters etc. 
+# 
+# Copyright (C) 2012 Seecr (Seek You Too B.V.) http://seecr.nl
+# Copyright (C) 2012 Stichting Bibliotheek.nl (BNL) http://www.bibliotheek.nl
